this_title: Learning To Live Together: The Return of Mad Dogs & Englishmen
introduction: Learning To Live Together: The Return of Mad Dogs & Englishmen is a documentary concert film telling the story of Joe Cocker’s historic “Mad Dogs & Englishmen” tour, featuring inspired performances from Leon Russell, Rita Coolidge, Chris Robinson (The Black Crowes), Dave Mason, and Claudia Lennear (20 Feet From Stardom).
